<!-- FAQ -->
<section id="faq">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">Common Questions</span>
      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <p>Everything you need to know about our printing services.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-grid">
      <div class="faq-item reveal">
        <div class="faq-question"><h3>What is your turnaround time?</h3><div class="faq-icon"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></div></div>
        <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Standard turnaround is 3–5 working days. We also offer express same-day or next-day printing for urgent orders at an additional charge. Contact us to discuss your timeline.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item reveal">
        <div class="faq-question"><h3>What file formats do you accept?</h3><div class="faq-icon"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></div></div>
        <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">We accept PDF, AI, PSD, EPS, and high-resolution JPG/PNG files. For best results, submit print-ready PDFs with 3mm bleed and CMYK colour mode. Our team can also help you prepare files.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item reveal">
        <div class="faq-question"><h3>Do you offer design services?</h3><div class="faq-icon"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></div></div>
        <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Yes! We have an in-house design team that can create or refine your artwork. Design fees vary by complexity. Orders above $150 include a free basic design service.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item reveal">
        <div class="faq-question"><h3>What is the minimum order quantity?</h3><div class="faq-icon"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></div></div>
        <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Minimum quantities vary by product. Name cards start from 50 pieces, flyers from 100 pieces, and t-shirts from 10 pieces. Contact us for specific product minimums.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item reveal">
        <div class="faq-question"><h3>Do you deliver to my location?</h3><div class="faq-icon"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></div></div>
        <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Yes, we offer delivery across Singapore. We also ship internationally to Malaysia, UAE, India, and other countries. Delivery charges apply based on order size and destination.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item reveal">
        <div class="faq-question"><h3>How do I get a quote?</h3><div class="faq-icon"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></div></div>
        <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Simply fill in the contact form below, WhatsApp us at +65 9875 1606, or call us directly. Tell us the product, quantity, size, and any special requirements and we'll get back to you within 2 hours.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item reveal">
        <div class="faq-question"><h3>Do you offer credit terms?</h3><div class="faq-icon"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></div></div>
        <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Yes, we offer credit terms for approved corporate accounts. Regular clients with a good payment history can apply for 30-day credit terms. Contact us to discuss eligibility.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item reveal">
        <div class="faq-question"><h3>What payment methods do you accept?</h3><div class="faq-icon"><i class="fas fa-plus"></i></div></div>
        <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">We currently accept PayNow and Bank Transfer. For walk-in orders, cash payment is also accepted. Corporate invoicing is available for approved accounts.</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

